entries.femaleVariant: So what? Just pays you up front, like a fuckin' gonk?
'Cept he doesn't know he's a gonk. Not at first. Then, slowly but surely, it'll dawn on him.
We're handlin' it... yeah... yeah... make a round of all NC...
What...? Oxymesteron? Oldie but a goodie, hehe? Sure it'll turn up somewhere.
See, you gotta work him first, establish trust...
What if he brings up the eddies?
You don't do shit... pretend like it never even crossed your mind, like you're not about that.
Then you tell him it's time to pay up. He doesn't wanna? Give 'im a 'lil scare. Moment he hands it over, he's your bitch for life.
Tell him to go steal from a buddy? Borrow from family? It's always, "Yes sir, right away!"
Give up the whole store, if you ask him to. So then what?
That's it. You got your cash-cow. You're set for life.
We'll see... sometime this week. Later.
Hey, what does a corpo say before he's about to off himself?
